  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "KNOCK-OUT ACTION FOR 2 PLAYERS AT ONCE!\n\nYour Mission...Seek out and destroy a group of ruthless villains who'll stop at nothing to wipe you off the map. Each brutal renegade is a wizard at martial arts and trick moves. You must battle six deadly foes until you confront your greatest challenge-their master, the diabolical C.J.\n\nPunch, leap, somersault and kick your way over skyscraper beams, through the jungle, gritty back alleys, a wrestling ring, the top of a truck, and more. You've never punched-up so much pure action and exciting game play.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
